{"tid":883281,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大嶼山長沙嶼南道住宅地1.6億元批出","createTime":"2018-10-30T17:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T22:32:45.000Z","uid":75877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fcb9d59b0fa03700581ea9f6beeeeb2d39ca2b27","tid":883281,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:07:08.000Z","msg":"地政總署公布，大嶼山長沙嶼南道一幅住宅用地，以1.6億元批予盛裕興業，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">作價低於市場預期下限的2.6億元。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n項目上周五截標，共收到6份標書。地皮可建總樓面約2.37萬平方呎，項目覆蓋率最大25%，建築物不可高於兩層，須於2023年6月底前完工。"},{"pid":"3cfe3bfa31e5bbcedfbdfc5277675de569a8c0bc","tid":883281,"uid":62935,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:39:58.000Z","msg":"好友當睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcdbd4dfbac4f7cb19f67e75cf00a5879653eec2","tid":883281,"uid":64345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T22:32:45.000Z","msg":"離島唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}